{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Seed Hunter is an action-packed Roguelite game. We strive to incorporate handcrafted animations, traditional Chinese gameplay design, and a variety of items and weapon choices.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1078490/extras/weapon1.gif?t=1737426716\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">7 Types and 37 Weapons</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Axe, Sword &amp; Shield, Dual Blades, Great Sword, Sword, Kunai, and Bow. We offer 37 different weapons across 7 categories.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1078490/extras/weapon2.gif?t=1737426716\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">For each weapon, you will have different skills. If you like it, why not make it stronger and play with it the way you enjoy?\u00a0</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Hundreds of Ability Cards, 8 Upgrade Paths</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">We have designed two different skill trees. You can add some skills from your base, which will make you stronger in your next adventure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">For your adventure, we have created more than 100 different skill cards that provide you with unlimited play styles, making you the strongest hunter we have ever seen.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1078490/extras/update.gif?t=1737426716\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Handcraft Animation in Seed Hunter</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Like our favorite game, Cuphead, we use handcrafted animation in Seed Hunter. We create every jump and slash ourselves from scratch. We hope it provides you with a splendid gaming experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"h